{"tid":431662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趕返學橫過馬路　17歲男生遭巴士撞傷昏迷","createTime":"2017-10-11T02:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T05:04:52.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9c8f2af5e261364e770e19f93713836b4f94a8","tid":431662,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:01:26.000Z","msg":"沙田小瀝源路培基書院對開，早上8時許，一名17歲男生橫過馬路返學途中，遭一輛駛經雙層巴士撞倒，受傷倒地昏迷不醒，數名路人見狀連忙上前協助，稍後再救護員到場將學生送院，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場是培基書院對開馬路，傷者正是該校學生，數名親友事後趕到醫院，校方正了解事件並提供協助。"},{"pid":"693a50dfde897a92ced0f9688f879af1a6184fa8","tid":431662,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171011&amp;guid=57316776&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171011%26guid%3D57316776%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=cgLin8mi%2F3i1FLjXw5KkwDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0b06aa07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20171011%26guid%3D57316776%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=cbf7b225\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20171011&amp;guid=57316776&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"12a5023c82b5c0a3dfe2f65b3e046f3c7de037c5","tid":431662,"uid":5077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"唔好有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842edf8ae4f20f0838b2c3bd34eb91b477e52861","tid":431662,"uid":151700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T02:05:53.000Z","msg":"我短跑攞第一嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16611ecee4726df8ef10e35f42d1dd474ff019c7","tid":431662,"uid":149575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1